# Read Me file
A read me is instructing someone else to read me. It provides basic information and contextual information to help someone else who wants to replicate or check your work. 

To see an example of an excellent read me file, see "zero sum report read me file": https://fripublichealth.quarto.pub/zerosum/readme-preview.html
